{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"content_hash":"e9327ecc68f2231d6395491d3d0ddb150c91a02a8468c32d33df024ed5b72039","digest":{"component_or_area":"Gerrit-side ticket-store writers / identity signing enforcement","key_entities":["identity.require_authenticated","review-bot","opcert-service","voter.py relates_to LINK","graph/_links.py","_seam.append_event","_GATE_EXEMPT_TYPES","verify_authorship.py","REBAR_SYNC_PUSH","REBAR_IDENTITY_SIGNING_KEY","fetch-secrets.sh","identity 594c","rebar verify-identity --require-authenticated","canary 1787","auto-lander (ADR-0047)","reconcile-bridge.yml"],"problem_keywords":["identity signing","authenticated writes","ticket store writer classification","canary verification","gate exemption","deployed vm signing","event verification"],"propositions":["Every Gerrit-side ticket-store operation must be enumerated and classified as non-writing, gate-exempt, or in-scope writer with file/line evidence.","opcert-service never writes to the shared store (REBAR_SYNC_PUSH=off), so it is unaffected by require_authenticated enforcement.","The review-bot code_review artifact is gate-exempt via _GATE_EXEMPT_TYPES and is not rejected under require_authenticated=true.","The only in-scope Gerrit-side writer is the review-bot's reciprocal relates_to LINK written onto the non-exempt work ticket, which must be signed as identity 594c.","Canary 1787 requires confirming the deployed-VM review-bot produces an actual signed and verified LINK event, not merely a materialized signing key.","The deployed review-bot was confirmed alive and produced a signed relates_to LINK on a non-exempt work ticket, satisfying the signing verification."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"TICKET_DIGEST","timestamp":1784253898989538001,"uuid":"446aa136-a75a-4cc0-af8a-70e57305903d"}